title: NFL ATL: Top 10 NFL players
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Top 10 NFL players
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest news from around the league including Josh Gordon's arrest, Jimmy Graham's contract situation, RGIII's reported return to 2012 form and  much more. The guys also reveal new players on "Making the Leap" before comparing top 10 NFL players lists.
